[4] Michigan (Detroit) ex overseas
Date: Fri 19 Jul 2019 08:10AM EDT
Source: Fox2 [abridged, edited]
http://www.fox2detroit.com/news/local-news/case-of-measles-confirmed-in-detroit-after-overseas-travel


The Detroit Health Department says a person who lives in Detroit has a confirmed case of the measles.

The patient has the measles after traveling overseas, though the department didn't specify where. The department also didn't specify how old the patient is.

